For the purposes of SCORE, to test ​H*​ in line with the original paper, [I/we] will use ​a linear 
mixed model with the ​lme4 ​package in ​R​ with crossed random effects for Participants, 
Items, and State. Specifically this model will include how disturbing the picture was for 
the dependent variable, which will be predicted by the type of picture seen with 
Non-COVID-Verbal as the comparison category. The code was replicated from the 
original study, only changing variable names to match our dataset.  
 
